            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            ><span
              >Is my personal information shared or sold to third parties?</span
            >
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5 duration-300 ease-out text-purple-500"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              ><path
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
            ></button
          ><div
            x-collapse=""
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            style="display: none;">
            <div class="text-gray-500 p-4 pt-2 text-sm">
              No, we strictly adhere to a privacy-centric approach. Your
              personal information is never shared, sold, or monetized. We
              prioritize your privacy and ensure that your data remains
              confidential and only accessible to you.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><div
          class="cursor-pointer group text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-500"
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-purple-900': activeAccordion==id, 'text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-500': activeAccordion!=id }">
          <button
            class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 pb-1 select-none text-left w-full text-sm lg:text-base"
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            ><span>Can I use this platform on multiple devices?</span>
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5 duration-300 ease-out text-purple-500"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              ><path
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
            ></button
          ><div
            x-collapse=""
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            style="display: none;">
            <div class="text-gray-500 p-4 pt-2 text-sm">
              Yes, you can access our platform on multiple devices. Your
              encrypted data remains synced across all devices, allowing you to
              seamlessly communicate and access your files and messages from
              anywhere.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><div
          class="cursor-pointer group text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-500"
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-purple-900': activeAccordion==id, 'text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-500': activeAccordion!=id }">
          <button
            class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 pb-1 select-none text-left w-full text-sm lg:text-base"
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            ><span
              >Are there any storage limitations for files and documents?</span
            >
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5 duration-300 ease-out text-purple-500"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              ><path
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
            ></button
          ><div
            x-collapse=""
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            style="display: none;">
            <div class="text-gray-500 p-4 pt-2 text-sm">
              Our platform provides ample storage space for your files and
              documents. However, there may be storage limitations based on the
              pricing plan you choose. We offer flexible plans to suit your
              needs and provide options to upgrade if you require additional
              storage capacity.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="cursor-pointer group text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-500"
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-purple-900': activeAccordion==id, 'text-gray-600 hover:text-purple-500': activeAccordion!=id }">
          <button
            class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 pb-1 select-none text-left w-full text-sm lg:text-base"
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            ><span>Is it possible to export my data from the platform?</span>
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5 duration-300 ease-out text-purple-500"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              ><path
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
            ></button
          ><div
            x-collapse=""
            x-show="activeAccordion==id"
            style="display: none;">
            <div class="text-gray-500 p-4 pt-2 text-sm">
              Yes, you can export your data from the platform. We offer export
              features that allow you to download your messages, files, and
              documents, ensuring you have a local copy for backup or migration
              purposes. It provides you with greater control and flexibility
              over your data.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
